WEBVTT

07:06.430 --> 07:07.280 line:80%
Really?

07:08.640 --> 07:10.520 line:80%
But I heard

07:10.630 --> 07:13.550 line:80%
that she supported
a scholar fiancé for years.

07:13.600 --> 07:15.150 line:80%
Once the scholar passed
the provincial exam,

07:15.150 --> 07:17.430 line:80%
he betrayed her
and broke off the engagement.
